  <thing id="raPTIceSpe" name="Ice Spear" description="As an immediate action, an ice devil can cause its {i}+2 frost spear{/i} to melt and a new one to instantly reappear in its hands. Mythic ice devils are particularly masterful at throwing their specially formed spears, treating these weapons as having a range increment of 50 feet." compset="RaceSpec" summary="As an immediate action, an ice devil can cause its {i}+2 frost spear{/i} to melt and a new one to instantly reappear in its hands.">
