  <thing id="raPTMaster" name="Mastermind" description="Once per day as a full-round action, an ice devil may link its mind with a willing humanoid creature by touching it for 1 full round. The target gains a +2 profane bonus to Intelligence and remains in constant telepathic contact with the ice devil for as long as the two creatures remain on the same plane. A creature can have a link with only one ice devil at a time. The connection is removed by {i}dispel evil{/i} or {i}dispel law{/i}. The ice devil can remove it as well as a free action (causing 2d6 Intelligence drain to the victim, no save)." compset="RaceSpec" summary="As a full-round action an ice devil may link its mind with a willing humanoid creature.">
