  <thing id="raPTSlow" name="Slow" description="A hit from an ice devil&apos;s tail or spear induces numbing cold. The opponent must succeed on a DC 23 Fortitude save or be affected as though by a {i}slow{/i} spell for 1d6 rounds. This effect comes from the devil in the case of its weapon; it is not a quality possessed by the spear itself. The save DC is Constitution-based." compset="RaceSpec" summary="A hit from an ice devil&apos;s tail or spear induces numbing cold.">
