  <thing id="raPTFilWea" name="Filthy Weapons" description="Decades of dirt cling to the ettin&apos;s flails and javelins, coating them with disease. Any creature struck by one of the mythic ettin&apos;s manufactured weapons must succeed on a Fortitude save or contract filth fever. {i}Filth Fever{/i}: {i}save{/i} Fort DC 19; {i}onset{/i} 1d3 days; {i}frequency{/i} 1/day; {i}effect{/i} 1d3 Dex damage and 1d3 Con damage; {i}cure{/i} 2 consecutive saves." compset="RaceSpec">
