  <thing id="raPTHyFaHe" name="Fast Healing" description="A hydra&apos;s fast healing ability is equal to its current number of heads (minimum fast healing 5). This fast healing applies only to damage inflicted on the hydra&apos;s body." compset="RaceSpec">
