  <thing id="raPTMazMas" name="Maze Mastery" description="A minotaur may designate an area no greater than 100 feet on a side as its personal domain (typically a maze or other confusing structure). As a move action, the minotaur can teleport from one point in its domain to any other point in its domain, as if using {i}greater teleport{/i}. In addition, whenever the minotaur must make a saving throw while inside its domain, it can roll twice and take the better result. A minotaur can change its domain once per week." compset="RaceSpec" summary="A minotaur may designate an area no greater than 100 feet on a side as its personal domain (typically a maze or other confusing structure).">
