  <thing id="rPTMyMummy" name="Mummy, Mythic" description="Created centuries ago and imbued with the most powerful of necromantic spells, the mythic mummy is the true master of the sands. Capable of shifting the desert at its whim, the mythic mummy is not content to rot for all time in its sandy tomb. Instead it is known to assume the guise of the living and bring its wasting sands to the homes and cities of the living it so despises.\n\nThe mythic mummy is over 6 feet tall and it weighs just over 300 pounds, mostly due to the sand and desiccated f lowers that fill its hollowed-out body." compset="Race">
