  <thing id="raPTCreSpa" name="Create Spawn" description="Upon killing a humanoid creature with a melee attack, a mythic mummy may expend one use of mythic power to instantly transform the slain creature into a mummy with the advanced creature template. Spawn are under the command of the mummy that created them, often believing themselves to be specific guards or members of the mummy&apos;s long-dead court. They remain enslaved until its death, at which point they become free-willed mummies. They do not possess any of the abilities they had in life." compset="RaceSpec">
