  <thing id="raPTDesMas" name="Desert Mastery" description="A mummy can command earth and sand within 100 feet to create a variety of spell-like effects. At will, as a standard action, a mummy can reduce rock to sand (with the same effect as {i}transmute rock to mud{/i}) or create lifelike shapes made from sand, which function exactly as the spell {i}major image{/i}. (These creations collapse if disbelieved or attacked.) Additionally, by expending one use of mythic power the mummy can summon a creature of living sand, which has the same statistics and abilities as a Large mud elemental ({i}Pathfinder RPG Bestiary 2{/i} 120). The mummy&apos;s caster level equals its Hit Dice for the purpose of these effects." compset="RaceSpec" summary="A mummy can command earth and sand within 100 feet to create a variety of spell-like effects.">
