  <thing id="raPTMuDesp" name="Despair" description="All creatures within a 30-foot radius that see a mummy must make a DC 18 Will save or be paralyzed by fear for 1d4 rounds. Whether or not the save is successful, that creature cannot be affected again by the same mummy&apos;s despair ability for 24 hours. This is a paralysis and a mind-affecting fear effect. The save DC is Charisma-based and includes a +2 racial modifier." compset="RaceSpec">
