  <thing id="rcPTItemCr" name="Itemcraft" description="You are skilled at getting the most out of magic items. You add 1/2 your mythic tier (minimum 1) to the caster level of potions, scrolls, staves, and wands you use when determining the effects of the spells created by them. When using a staff, wand, or other charged item, you can expend one use of mythic power in place of one charge." compset="RaceCustom" summary="You are skilled at getting the most out of magic items." uniqueness="unique">
