  <thing id="rcPTAllDef" name="Ally Defense" description="You can expend one use of mythic power as an immediate action whenever a melee attack is declared against an adjacent ally. The attacking creature must roll twice on its attack roll and take the worse result. In addition, the target of the attack gains an insight bonus to its AC equal to your tier until the start of its next turn." compset="RaceCustom" summary="You can expend one use of mythic power as an immediate action whenever a melee attack is declared against an adjacent ally." uniqueness="unique">
