  <thing id="rcPTCatHaz" name="Catch Hazard" description="You can prevent area of effect traps (including rock falls, avalanches, and natural traps) from harming adjacent allies. If you are in the area of effect or adjacent to a square or ally affected by the trap, you attempt a Reflex saving throw using the trap&apos;s save DC. If the trap normally makes an attack roll, the save DC is 10 + the bonus on the attack roll. If you succeed on your Reflex save, none of your adjacent allies takes any damage and you take half damage. If you fail your Reflex save, you and your allies are affected normally." compset="RaceCustom" summary="You can prevent area of effect traps (including rock falls, avalanches, and natural traps) from harming adjacent allies" uniqueness="unique">
