  <thing id="rcPTQuiRec" name="Quick Recovery" description="Whenever you are subject to a spell, spell-like ability, or special ability that imposes one of the following conditions the duration of those conditions is halved: dazed, dazzled, deafened, sickened, and stunned. You can take this ability twice. The second time you take this ability, it also applies to blinded, nauseated, and paralyzed. Any other effects related to these spell or ability that caused the condition is unaffected." compset="RaceCustom" summary="Whenever you are subject to a spell, spell-like ability, or special ability that imposes one of the following conditions the duration of those conditions is halved:" maxlimit="2">
