  <thing id="rcPTUnmove" name="Unmoveable" description="Add your guardian tier to your CMD whenever an enemy attempts a bull rush, pull, reposition, or trip combat maneuver against you. If the maneuver succeeds, you can expend one use of mythic power as an immediate action to cause it to fail instead." compset="RaceCustom" summary="Add your guardian tier to your CMD whenever an enemy attempts a bull rush, pull, reposition, or trip combat maneuver against you." uniqueness="useronce">
